snippet.title: Eternal Dungeon - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Eternal Dungeon is a fantasy themed auto-scroller. Jump, slide, and slash your way through nine levels as you descend deeper into the dungeon.

Available for PC through Steam on October 24th!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1445400/Eternal_Dungeon/
